      <title>融化的永久冻土使“醉林”储存的碳减少</title>
      <link>https://www.newscientist.com/article/2458932-melting-permafrost-makes-drunken-forests-store-less-carbon/?utm_campaign=RSS%7CNSNS&amp;utm_source=NSNS&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_content=news</link>
